              "free_text": [
                "Inertial confinement experiments were",
                "conducted at the National Ignition Facility.",
                "Temporally shaped laser beams were used to generate a",
                "soft x-ray field that ablatively imploded a spherical",
                "plastic capsule filled with 99.9% tritium gas (0.1%",
                "deuterium)."
              ]
            }
          ],
